channel.title: Project DungeonFest run.bat error
channel.description:
hey so i just downloaded project dungeonfest and was really excited only to find out...i get the same error as with other great sources.
when i click run.bat in the source, it says:
Error occurred during initialization of VM java/lang/NoClassDefFoundError: java/lang/Object Press any key to continue...
I have searched and one forum said it might be the class path variable not set right, but my 317 servers all work fine?
If anyone can help I'll appreciate it so much and I'll make u co-owner or something in return. I just really need this done :(
